I [[San]] '''Francisco de Sales''', [[Oratory of Saint Philip Neri|C.O.]], [[Minim (religious order)|T.O.M.]], [[Order of Friars Minor Capuchin|A.O.F.M. Cap.]] ({{lang-fr|François de Sales}}) (21 Agosto 1567{{spaced ndash}}28 Diciembre 1622) metung yang [[Romano Catolicong Diosesis ning Lausanne, Geneva and Fribourg|Obispo ning Geneva]] a [[santo]] king [[Iglesia Catolica]]. Mekilala ya king kayang malalam a kasalpantayanan ampo king kayang malumeng pamanarap kareng pamipitna-pitnang relihyosung dela ning [[Protestant Reformation]]. Pikabalwan ya murin kareng kayang kasulatan king paksa ning direksyong espiritwal ampong pamanalkus a espiritwal He is known also for his writings on the topic of spiritual direction and (''spiritual formation''), partikular king ''[[Introduction to the Devout Life]]'' ampo ing ''Treatise on the Love of God''.

